		<td colspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" width="100%" valign=top style="text-align: justify; 
		" 
			>
			<BR>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<P>
<HR>
</P>
<P><BR>1. What should the % increase be for the healing side?</P>
<P>I would be satisfied with +25% IF we also gained some other useful healing tools, ie. HoTs, group heals/cures, Crit heals on KR. Make them only useable in defensive stance even.</P>
<P>2. What additional healing tools (spells, skills) do we need? </P>
<P>See above</P>
<P><BR>3. What should the % increase be for the DPS side, and what spells does it apply to?</P>
<P><!-- / message -->Even here, I think that 25% is sufficient IF it applies to ALL detrimental spells and maybe even get a mana cost reduction while in offensive stance.<BR></P>
<P>
<HR>
</P></BLOCKQUOTE><BR>
